Title: Best Laid Plans
Description:
Fyrakk may be brash, but he is not a fool. If we are to save the Dream, we must undermine his plans as quickly as possible.

At their core, the Primalists are unorganized. Infiltrate their camp and search for any clues or information.

The more information we have, the sooner we can take down Fyrakk once and for all.
ObjectivesText: Collect 4 clues in the Primalist Stronghold.
